  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a pandemonium world in <i>Tiny Chaos</i>, a bullet heaven survival game that will test your wits, reflexes, and endurance. Face relentless hordes of enemies, explore vibrant stages, and unlock the full potential of your characters in this chaotic journey to survive against all odds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Levels and Stages</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a variety of stages, each offering unique environments and interactive elements. Every stage presents new ways to test your skills. Select your difficulty from Easy to Hard or push your limits with Insane and Chaos levels, designed for those who crave the ultimate challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/e619c2180ddcb3e11aeae5ce1d95d11f.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/e619c2180ddcb3e11aeae5ce1d95d11f.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/e619c2180ddcb3e11aeae5ce1d95d11f.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Characters with Distinct Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain all powerful characters, each with their own playstyle, abilities, and skills. Level them up, upgrade their weapons, and create devastating skill builds to conquer every stage and difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/208fe4b06d360f0abcc604877d30e109.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/208fe4b06d360f0abcc604877d30e109.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/208fe4b06d360f0abcc604877d30e109.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquer Chaos with Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why face chaos alone when you can bring your friends? With the co-op feature, team up to tackle stages together, cover each other’s backs, and defeat bosses as a team. Chaos is better shared!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/c948bf68e31fb35ae4a4010e2567ffe3.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/c948bf68e31fb35ae4a4010e2567ffe3.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/c948bf68e31fb35ae4a4010e2567ffe3.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb the Leaderboards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove your might! As you perfect your builds and optimize your damage output, compete for glory by climbing the leaderboards. Show off your record-breaking scores and claim your title as the ultimate survivor.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/34ab58bf86c91538f967c8969548a4b7.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/34ab58bf86c91538f967c8969548a4b7.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/34ab58bf86c91538f967c8969548a4b7.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unstoppable Waves of Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The longer you survive, the harder it gets. As waves of enemies grow in size and strength, adapt your strategy by collecting buffs and powering up your character builds. Can you withstand the unrelenting chaos?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/026f028b3ffd2f832e7441360117191a.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/026f028b3ffd2f832e7441360117191a.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/026f028b3ffd2f832e7441360117191a.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a pandemonium world in <i>Tiny Chaos</i>, a bullet heaven survival game that will test your wits, reflexes, and endurance. Face relentless hordes of enemies, explore vibrant stages, and unlock the full potential of your characters in this chaotic journey to survive against all odds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Levels and Stages</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a variety of stages, each offering unique environments and interactive elements. Every stage presents new ways to test your skills. Select your difficulty from Easy to Hard or push your limits with Insane and Chaos levels, designed for those who crave the ultimate challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/e619c2180ddcb3e11aeae5ce1d95d11f.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/e619c2180ddcb3e11aeae5ce1d95d11f.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/e619c2180ddcb3e11aeae5ce1d95d11f.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Characters with Distinct Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain all powerful characters, each with their own playstyle, abilities, and skills. Level them up, upgrade their weapons, and create devastating skill builds to conquer every stage and difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/208fe4b06d360f0abcc604877d30e109.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/208fe4b06d360f0abcc604877d30e109.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/208fe4b06d360f0abcc604877d30e109.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquer Chaos with Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why face chaos alone when you can bring your friends? With the co-op feature, team up to tackle stages together, cover each other’s backs, and defeat bosses as a team. Chaos is better shared!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/c948bf68e31fb35ae4a4010e2567ffe3.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/c948bf68e31fb35ae4a4010e2567ffe3.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/c948bf68e31fb35ae4a4010e2567ffe3.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb the Leaderboards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove your might! As you perfect your builds and optimize your damage output, compete for glory by climbing the leaderboards. Show off your record-breaking scores and claim your title as the ultimate survivor.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/34ab58bf86c91538f967c8969548a4b7.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/34ab58bf86c91538f967c8969548a4b7.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/34ab58bf86c91538f967c8969548a4b7.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unstoppable Waves of Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The longer you survive, the harder it gets. As waves of enemies grow in size and strength, adapt your strategy by collecting buffs and powering up your character builds. Can you withstand the unrelenting chaos?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/026f028b3ffd2f832e7441360117191a.poster.avif?t=1739443894\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/026f028b3ffd2f832e7441360117191a.webm?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500680/extras/026f028b3ffd2f832e7441360117191a.mp4?t=1739443894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
